you with your bag.

00:27:05.458 --> 00:27:07.326 align:middle line:84%
They will chat you up and
they'll flirt with you.

00:27:07.326 --> 00:27:09.495 align:middle line:84%
And you're like, "This
doesn't happen at home."

00:27:09.495 --> 00:27:11.564 align:middle line:84%
It's not that the
world has changed

00:27:11.564 --> 00:27:13.132 align:middle line:84%
and that you must go
traveling in order

00:27:13.132 --> 00:27:15.901 align:middle line:84%
to experience the beauty
of humanity; it's the fact

00:27:15.901 --> 00:27:18.237 align:middle line:84%
that you became beautiful
because you became curious.

00:27:18.237 --> 00:27:21.006 align:middle line:84%
And we're not curious
when we're at home.

00:27:21.006 --> 00:27:23.642 align:middle line:84%
And by being curious, all of
the things that we're kind

00:27:23.642 --> 00:27:25.811 align:middle line:90%
of looking for start to find us.

00:27:25.811 --> 00:27:29.815 align:middle line:84%
And it's just such a wonderful
thing to do in your hometown

00:27:29.815 --> 00:27:33.052 align:middle line:84%
because all of the love and
excitement that you experience

00:27:33.052 --> 00:27:35.454 align:middle line:84%
when you're out traveling
the world comes to you

00:27:35.454 --> 00:27:36.756 align:middle line:90%
because you're being curious.

00:27:36.756 --> 00:27:38.924 align:middle line:84%
You're becoming the
person who is the traveler,

00:27:38.924 --> 00:27:40.526 align:middle line:84%
but you're doing
it in your home.

00:27:40.526 --> 00:27:41.927 align:middle line:90%
It's lovely.

00:27:41.927 --> 00:27:45.431 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Protection, is there
anything as such as protection

00:27:45.431 --> 00:27:47.933 align:middle line:84%
that you feel you
need or call forth?

00:27:47.933 --> 00:27:50.236 align:middle line:84%
