of my pet [inaudible]

00:27:50.236 --> 00:27:53.839 align:middle line:84%
because it's the same thing
as when you're unhappy,

00:27:53.839 --> 00:27:55.841 align:middle line:90%
being unhappy about it.

00:27:55.841 --> 00:27:58.144 align:middle line:84%
So it's like when you believe
that you need protection,

00:27:58.144 --> 00:28:01.046 align:middle line:84%
then you are in the
consciousness of the energy

00:28:01.046 --> 00:28:04.784 align:middle line:84%
that you are in fear, and then
you're completely in alignment

00:28:04.784 --> 00:28:06.385 align:middle line:84%
with the idea that
you need protection.

00:28:06.385 --> 00:28:08.454 align:middle line:84%
Then therefore, you're open
to the thing that you need

00:28:08.454 --> 00:28:09.822 align:middle line:90%
to protect yourself against.

00:28:09.822 --> 00:28:11.090 align:middle line:90%
It's very interesting.

00:28:11.090 --> 00:28:13.225 align:middle line:84%
There's a little
apple pip experiment

00:28:13.225 --> 00:28:16.128 align:middle line:84%
where you get some
pips from the inside

00:28:16.128 --> 00:28:17.997 align:middle line:84%
of an apple and let
them dry out.

00:28:17.997 --> 00:28:20.299 align:middle line:90%
Then you open a fresh apple --

00:28:20.299 --> 00:28:22.234 align:middle line:84%
it sounds like open
it like it's a jar.

00:28:22.234 --> 00:28:26.438 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, you slice open an apple
and you put the apple pips

00:28:26.438 --> 00:28:29.708 align:middle line:84%
on white paper about an
inch away from each other.

00:28:29.708 --> 00:28:31.777 align:middle line:84%
You'll start to see that the
healthy apple pips have kind of,

00:28:31.777 --> 00:28:34.814 align:middle line:84%
like, a white line around
them, like a circle.

00:28:34.814 --> 00:28:36.382 align:middle line:90%
And in sense you could say

00:28:36.382 --> 00:28:38.984 align:middle line:84%
that that's the energetic
aura of the apple pips.

00:28:38.984 --> 00:28:41.220 align:middle line:84%
And then, as you kind of,
like, rest your eyes and kind

00:28:41.220 --> 00:28:43.155 align:middle line:84%
of just stare in
between the two of them,

00:28:43.155 --> 00:28:47.193 align:middle line:84%
you'll see a white line
going towards the drying

00:28:47.193 --> 00:28:49.995 align:middle line:84%
out apple pips from
the healthy apple pips.

00:28:49.995 --> 00:28:51.597 align:middle line:90%
So what this tells me --

00:28:51.597 --> 00:28:53.999 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Doing all those
interesting experiment,

00:28:53.999 --> 00:28:55.100 align:middle line:90%
aren't you?

00:28:55.100 --> 00:28:56.368 align:middle line:84%
>> BW: I just have a
very scientific mind.

00:28:56.368 --> 00:28:58.404 align:middle line:84%
And I'm just never
willing to kind of, like,

00:28:58.404 --> 00:29:02.441 align:middle line:84%
take things at sort of
face value, which is why

00:29:02.441 --> 00:29:04.176 align:middle line:90%
in  You Do Know  it's all

00:29:04.176 --> 00:29:06.812 align:middle line:84%
about how this works,
not just it works.

00:29:06.812 --> 00:29:08.080 align:middle line:90%
It's how it works.

00:29:08.080 --> 00:29:10.916 align:middle line:84%
I've copied it up with
neuroscience, and psychology,

00:29:10.916 --> 00:29:14.119 align:middle line:84%
and medical science, and pulled
all of these pieces together

00:29:14.119 --> 00:29:16.755 align:middle line:84%
to actually make a
very defined picture.

00:29:16.755 --> 00:29:20.125 align:middle line:84%
And so what the apple pip
experiment tells us is

00:29:20.125 --> 00:29:22.795 align:middle line:84%
that when we are, say for
example, visiting somebody

00:29:22.795 --> 00:29:25.464 align:middle line:84%
in hospital or we're with
a friend who's moaning --

00:29:25.464 --> 00:29:27.533 align:middle line:84%
welcome to England -- if we're
with a friend who's moaning

00:29:27.533 --> 00:29:30.636 align:middle line:90%
or things that are difficult,

00:29:30.636 --> 00:29:33.072 align:middle line:84%
we are actually giving
away our energy.

00:29:33.072 --> 00:29:34.640 align:middle line:84%
There's no such thing
as energy vampires.

00:29:34.640 --> 00:29:35.975 align:middle line:90%
They're not sucking.

00:29:35.975 --> 00:29:38.410 align:middle line:84%
You know, we are actually
giving away our energy

00:29:38.410 --> 00:29:39.778 align:middle line:90%
with our own free will.

00:29:39.778 --> 00:29:41.046 align:middle line:84%
And then we walk
away and go, "My God,

00:29:41.046 --> 00:29:42.548 align:middle line:90%
that person's exhausting."

00:29:42.548 --> 00:29:45.951 align:middle line:84%
And in actual fact, it was us
that was allowing ourselves

00:29:45.951 --> 00:29:47.319 align:middle line:90%
to give away that energy.

00:29:47.319 --> 00:29:48.520 align:middle line:90%
So literally when we're talking

00:29:48.520 --> 00:29:51.390 align:middle line:84%
about protection I
would say care less.

00:29:51.390 --> 00:29:53.359 align:middle line:90%
Stop caring.

00:29:53.359 --> 00:29:54.927 align:middle line:90%
If you stop caring about people,

00:29:54.927 --> 00:29:56.562 align:middle line:84%
then you'll stop
giving away your energy.

00:29:56.562 --> 00:29:58.831 align:middle line:84%
But good luck with that because
we're biologically designed

00:29:58.831 --> 00:29:59.965 align:middle line:90%
to care.

00:29:59.965 --> 00:30:02.101 align:middle line:84%
So the main thing is, is
how much are you caring?

00:30:02.101 --> 00:30:05.070 align:middle line:84%
How active is your solar plexus
frisking people for information

00:30:05.070 --> 00:30:06.972 align:middle line:84%
to see if the world's
a scary place?

00:30:06.972 --> 00:30:10.075 align:middle line:84%
You know? So the more
we believe in ourselves,

00:30:10.075 --> 00:30:11.810 align:middle line:84%
the less our energy
can be drained.

00:30:11.810 --> 00:30:14.713 align:middle line:84%
So the best form of protection
is believing in yourself

00:30:14.713 --> 00:30:16.649 align:middle line:84%
and not believing that you
need to turn around three times

00:30:16.649 --> 00:30:18.684 align:middle line:84%
and spit or cover
yourself in white light.

00:30:18.684 --> 00:30:21.520 align:middle line:84%
It's really just about knowing
in your heart, "I am okay,

00:30:21.520 --> 00:30:23.489 align:middle line:84%
and the universe loves
me, and I am safe."

00:30:23.489 --> 00:30:25.457 align:middle line:84%
That's all you really
need to know.

00:30:25.457 --> 00:30:29.461 align:middle line:84%
And so putting on protection
actually says the opposite.

00:30:29.461 --> 00:30:29.962 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Brilliant.

